flowchart LR
  User[User Browser] --> Frontend[React + Tailwind Frontend]
  Frontend -->|JSON or multipart form data| Backend[Express Backend]
  Backend --> Routes[Summarization Routes]
  Routes --> Services[Business Services]
  Services --> PDF[pdf-parse PDF Extraction]
  Services --> Processing[Text Preprocessing + Keywords]
  Processing --> AI[AI Engine Layer]
  AI --> OpenAI[OpenAI API]
  AI --> HF[Optional HuggingFace Script]
  OpenAI --> Backend
  HF --> Backend
  Backend -->|Summary, keywords, stats| Frontend
